name: Ext_R4B_TestReport_testScript
title: Cross-version Extension for R4B.TestReport.testScript for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version extension represents TestReport.testScript from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/TestReport|4.3.0 for use in FHIR R5.

element.short: Reference to the  version-specific TestScript that was executed to produce this TestReport
element.definition: Ideally this is an absolute URL that is used to identify the version-specific TestScript that was executed, matching the `TestScript.url`.
element.comment: `TestReport.testScript` maps to R5 `TestReport.testScript`. Has no type mapping So is mapped as SourceIsBroaderThanTarget.
